The location of the hotel is teriffic.	The rooms are elegent and quiet.	The service is exellent.	The swimming pool/sauna suite is lovely and relaxing.	The room was fine and the breakfast which was included in the price was excellent.	The front desk staff were very helpful and accomodating!	Staff were exceptionally helpful and pleasant.	The Kempinski is a lovely hotel located perfectly for tourists.	The hotel was easy to find, the staff friendly and I slept well.	This was a great choice of hotel.